    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving masterpiece. Under the hood, the S54 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and Double-VANOS variable valve timing, providing immediate throttle response and a screaming 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term chassis rigidity, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the suspension utilizes a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup for precise lateral grip. Recent service includes a full valve lash adjustment and a cooling system overhaul with a high-flow water pump. While showing minor aesthetic wear, the drivetrain is dialed in for performance driving, offering a visceral, analog experience with exceptional balance.",
