      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2019 Audi A6 3.0T Premium Plus. This vehicle is finished in a timeless Glacier White Metallic with a Black Valcona leather interior. Having been garage-kept, the paint retains a high-gloss finish, though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel consistent with daily use. Inside, the cabin is in excellent shape; the leather is supple with no tears, and the dual-screen MMI touch response system functions flawlessly. This A6 is powered by a smooth turbocharged V6 and features the legendary Quattro all-wheel-drive system. Recent service includes a fresh oil change, new cabin air filters, and a brake fluid flush. The tires have approximately 6/32nds of tread depth remaining. It comes with a clean title, two key fobs, and a comprehensive folder of service records from the last three years. This is a reliable, high-performance sedan that offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
